  "page": "A Storm of Swords-Chapter 32",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;background-color:rgb(35, 135, 75)\">Tyrion IV</th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords\" title=\"A Storm of Swords\">A Storm of Swords</a></i> chapter</td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" class=\"infobox-image\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<a href=\"/index.php/A_storm_of_swords\" title=\"A storm of swords\"><img alt=\"AStormOfSwords.jpg\" src=\"/images/thumb/2/24/AStormOfSwords.jpg/220px-AStormOfSwords.jpg\" width=\"220\" height=\"353\" class=\"thumbborder\" srcset=\"/images/2/24/AStormOfSwords.jpg 1.5x\" /></a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">POV</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Tyrion_Lannister\" title=\"Tyrion Lannister\">Tyrion</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Place</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/King%27s_Landing\" title=\"King&#39;s Landing\">King's Landing</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Page</th><td>\n352 <small>UK HC</small> <small>(<a href=\"/index.php/Chapters_Table_of_contents\" title=\"Chapters Table of contents\">Other versions</a>)</small></td></tr><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;background-color:rgb(35, 135, 75)\">Chapter chronology <small>(<a href=\"/index.php/Chapters\" title=\"Chapters\">All</a>)</small></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords-Chapter_19\" title=\"A Storm of Swords-Chapter 19\">Tyrion III</a><br />↑</td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<table style=\"width:100%;\"><tbody><tr>\n<td style=\"width:33%; text-align:center; vertical-align:middle;\"><a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords-Chapter_31\" title=\"A Storm of Swords-Chapter 31\">Jaime IV</a></td>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:middle;\">&#160;←</td>\n<td style=\"width:33%; text-align:center; vertical-align:middle; padding-right:0.1em; padding-left:0.1em;\"><a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Tyrion IV</a></td>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:middle;\">→&#160;</td>\n<td style=\"width:33%; text-align:center; vertical-align:middle;\"><a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords-Chapter_33\" title=\"A Storm of Swords-Chapter 33\">Samwell II</a></td>\n</tr></tbody></table></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n↓<br /><a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords-Chapter_38\" title=\"A Storm of Swords-Chapter 38\">Tyrion V</a></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Synopsis\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Synopsis</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Character_List_appearing.2Fmentioned\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Character List appearing/mentioned</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#Places_and_terms_mentioned\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Places and terms mentioned</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#References_and_Notes\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References and Notes</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Synopsis\">Synopsis</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=A_Storm_of_Swords-Chapter_32&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Synopsis\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p><a href=\"/index.php/Tyrion_Lannister\" title=\"Tyrion Lannister\">Tyrion</a> visits <a href=\"/index.php/Symon_Silvertongue\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Symon Silvertongue\">Symon Silvertongue</a>, and thinks to pay him to leave <a href=\"/index.php/King%27s_Landing\" title=\"King&#39;s Landing\">King's Landing</a>. But the singer wishes to join the tournament of singers that will take place during <a href=\"/index.php/Joffrey_Baratheon\" title=\"Joffrey Baratheon\">Joffrey</a>’s wedding. He blackmails Tyrion by indicating that he will tell about his relation with <a href=\"/index.php/Shae\" title=\"Shae\">Shae</a>. Tyrion promises him that one of the other singers will be removed, and <a href=\"/index.php/Bronn\" title=\"Bronn\">Bronn</a> will visit him in three days' time. Outside, Tyrion orders Bronn to kill Symon. \n</p><p>Later, <a href=\"/index.php/Tywin_Lannister\" title=\"Tywin Lannister\">Tyrion's father</a> shows him the two new <a href=\"/index.php/Valyrian_steel\" title=\"Valyrian steel\">Valyrian</a> swords he had made for Joffrey and <a href=\"/index.php/Jaime_Lannister\" title=\"Jaime Lannister\">Jaime</a>. Master <a href=\"/index.php/Tobho_Mott\" title=\"Tobho Mott\">Tobho Mott</a> reworked the metal, and the color of the blade on each sword is black and red. <a href=\"/index.php/House_Lannister\" title=\"House Lannister\">House Lannister</a> has not had a Valyrian sword in hundreds of years, and try as he might, Tywin could never get any of the lesser houses to sell theirs. Where the steel for these new swords came from is not revealed. Tywin tells him that he must consummate his marriage to <a href=\"/index.php/Sansa_Stark\" title=\"Sansa Stark\">Sansa</a>, and that <a href=\"/index.php/Mace_Tyrell\" title=\"Mace Tyrell\">Mace Tyrell</a> rejected the marriage proposal between <a href=\"/index.php/Cersei_Lannister\" title=\"Cersei Lannister\">Cersei</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/Willas_Tyrell\" title=\"Willas Tyrell\">Willas</a>, probably because the <a href=\"/index.php/Olenna_Redwyne\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Olenna Redwyne\">Queen of Thorns</a> told him to. \n</p><p><a href=\"/index.php/Pycelle\" title=\"Pycelle\">Pycelle</a> brings dire tidings from <a href=\"/index.php/The_Wall\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"The Wall\">the Wall</a>, and that Maester <a href=\"/index.php/Aemon_Targaryen_(son_of_Maekar_I)\" title=\"Aemon Targaryen (son of Maekar I)\">Aemon</a> fears Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Jeor_Mormont\" title=\"Jeor Mormont\">Mormont</a> is dead. Tywin tells Pycelle to send a veiled message that no men shall be sent to the Wall unless <a href=\"/index.php/Janos_Slynt\" title=\"Janos Slynt\">Janos Slynt</a> is considered for the post of <a href=\"/index.php/Lord_Commander_of_the_Night%27s_Watch\" title=\"Lord Commander of the Night&#39;s Watch\">Lord Commander of the Night's Watch</a>. Tyrion thinks to himself that he should have had Slynt and Pycelle put to death when he had the chance.\n</p>\n<h2><span id=\"Character_List_appearing/mentioned\"></span><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Character_List_appearing.2Fmentioned\">Character List appearing/mentioned</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=A_Storm_of_Swords-Chapter_32&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Character List appearing/mentioned\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div style=\"column-count:3; column-width:300px;\"> \n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/Tyrion_Lannister\" title=\"Tyrion Lannister\">Tyrion Lannister</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Symon_Silvertongue\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Symon Silvertongue\">Symon Silvertongue</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Joffrey_Baratheon\" title=\"Joffrey Baratheon\">Joffrey Baratheon</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Shae\" title=\"Shae\">Shae</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Bronn\" title=\"Bronn\">Bronn</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Tywin_Lannister\" title=\"Tywin Lannister\">Tywin Lannister</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Jaime_Lannister\" title=\"Jaime Lannister\">Jaime Lannister</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Tobho_Mott\" title=\"Tobho Mott\">Tobho Mott</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Sansa_Stark\" title=\"Sansa Stark\">Sansa Stark</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Mace_Tyrell\" title=\"Mace Tyrell\">Mace Tyrell</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Cersei_Lannister\" title=\"Cersei Lannister\">Cersei Lannister</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Willas_Tyrell\" title=\"Willas Tyrell\">Willas Tyrell</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Olenna_Redwyne\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Olenna Redwyne\">Olenna Redwyne</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Pycelle\" title=\"Pycelle\">Pycelle</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Aemon_Targaryen_(son_of_Maekar_I)\" title=\"Aemon Targaryen (son of Maekar I)\">Aemon Targaryen (son of Maekar I)</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Jeor_Mormont\" title=\"Jeor Mormont\">Jeor Mormont</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Janos_Slynt\" title=\"Janos Slynt\">Janos Slynt</a></li></ul>\n</div>\t\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Places_and_terms_mentioned\">Places and terms mentioned</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=A_Storm_of_Swords-Chapter_32&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Places and terms mentioned\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div style=\"column-count:3; column-width:300px;\"> \n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/King%27s_Landing\" title=\"King&#39;s Landing\">King's Landing</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Valyrian_steel\" title=\"Valyrian steel\">Valyrian steel</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Lannister\" title=\"House Lannister\">House Lannister</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/The_Wall\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"The Wall\">The Wall</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Lord_Commander_of_the_Night%27s_Watch\" title=\"Lord Commander of the Night&#39;s Watch\">Lord Commander of the Night's Watch</a></li></ul>\n</div>\n<p><br />\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References_and_Notes\">References and Notes</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=A_Storm_of_Swords-Chapter_32&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References and Notes\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li>The synopsis was copied from Aol member vbkorik27 previously at<a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external autonumber\" href=\"http://web.archive.org/web/20080228051425/members.aol.com/vbkorik27/summary/legend.html\">[1]</a></li>\n<li><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.tor.com/blogs/2013/02/a-read-of-ice-and-fire-a-storm-of-swords-part-18\">A Read of Ice and Fire: A Storm of Swords, Part 18</a>. Analyses and summary of the chapter by Leigh Butler.</li>\n<li><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://slynt.blogspot.se/2013/11/re-read-tyrion-iv-of-gold-and-mud-part-i.html\">Re-read Tyrion, IV: Of gold and mud - Part I</a>. Summary and analyses of the chapter in the course of a 10th reread by Slynt.</li>\n<li><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://slynt.blogspot.se/2013/11/re-read-tyrion-iv-of-gold-and-mud-part.html\">Re-read Tyrion, IV: Of gold and mud - Part II</a>. Summary and analyses of the chapter in the course of a 10th reread by Slynt.</li></ul>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260403152520\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.056 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.220 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 242/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 1104/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 8242/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 1421/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 8/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion dept